    <tier id="COLLOQ_ROG-dialog-0015" speaker="ROG-dialog-0015" category="colloq" type="a" display-name="ROG-dialog-0015 [colloq]">
      <event start="T1-407" end="T1">Ki() eee ki() </event>
      <event start="T1" end="T3-606">kje sma zdaj ostala? </event>
      <event start="T4-688" end="T5-234">Pr ovčkah, </event>
      <event start="T5-234" end="T5-582">ja. </event>
      <event start="T6-575" end="T2">A veš, </event>
      <event start="T2" end="T3">kaj imam? </event>
      <event start="T3" end="T9-312">Zdej, zdej sem eee ... </event>
      <event start="T9-312" end="T11-283">Ta prvu sem štiri kupu. </event>
      <event start="T11-798" end="T16-599">Pred štirimi leti, da bojo mi tisto v() vrt gor popasle, </event>
      <event start="T16-599" end="T17-152">ne. </event>
      <event start="T17-152" end="T18-844">Da bojo vrt popasle. </event>
      <event start="T18-844" end="T21-301">Seveda pa js p() pa ljubitelj sem tega, </event>
      <event start="T21-301" end="T22-244">k js sem mel, </event>
      <event start="T22-244" end="T23-484">se spomniš dobru, </event>
      <event start="T24-019" end="T26-017">pred sedmimi leti petindevetdeset plemenskih že ovc, </event>
      <event start="T26-017" end="T28-382">ne. </event>
      <event start="T28-382" end="T4">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T4" end="T5">ken potem sem pa s mislu, </event>
      <event start="T5" end="T31-558">bom to, </event>
      <event start="T31-558" end="T6">de mi vrt popase, </event>
      <event start="T6" end="T8">pa bom jes to potem ve() eee v jesen poklal, </event>
      <event start="T8" end="T7">pa v skrinju pa kašnemu prijatelju še, </event>
      <event start="T7" end="T39-875">ne? </event>
      <event start="T40-283" end="T41-868">Pa m spet drugu ljetu to ... </event>
      <event start="T42-428" end="T44-147">o() o() spet ... </event>
      <event start="T44-147" end="T9">Tako, </event>
      <event start="T9" end="T10">ja, ja, </event>
      <event start="T10" end="T46-604">tako. </event>
      <event start="T46-604" end="T11">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T11" end="T12">k() in iz tega ni blo pa potem nič. </event>
      <event start="T12" end="T13">Pa pršla jesen, </event>
      <event start="T13" end="T53-42">kovčke so ble stare sedem, kosem mescov. </event>
      <event start="T53-42" end="T56-345">So mele vse prek št@rdeset kil, </event>
      <event start="T56-345" end="T14">so so mele že ž() ž() žive teže, </event>
      <event start="T14" end="T58-556">sem rjeku, ja pa to. </event>
      <event start="T58-556" end="T15">Pa za mene bi p() </event>
      <event start="T15" end="T16">osebno bi jest to rabu, </event>
