      <event start="T119" end="T118">k tud ne ba() šparaš, </event>
      <event start="T118" end="T340-608">nč ne delam tagga s to ... </event>
      <event start="T340-608" end="T120">Po me je pa dala na ... h unmu kostolomcu Hadžiću, </event>
