      <event start="T142" end="T395-349">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T396-003" end="T143">Pa jaz sem reku: </event>
      <event start="T143" end="T398-076">"Jaz to ne morem še it." </event>
      <event start="T398-076" end="T399-931">"Kakšna druga varianta?" </event>
