      <event start="T1370-722" end="T529">Eee tam smo čaj spili. </event>
      <event start="T529" end="T598">Ono petnajst, dvajset minut </event>
      <event start="T598" end="T530">in zdaj pa gremo. </event>
      <event start="T530" end="T1376-882">Jaz nisem mogel vstati. </event>
      <event start="T1378-482" end="T1379-683">Pa mulec. </event>
      <event start="T1379-683" end="T531">Nič me ni bolelo. </event>
      <event start="T531" end="T1382-814">Eee mišice zakrknile. </event>
      <event start="T1390-462" end="T1391-525">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1394-866" end="T1396-562">Aja. </event>
      <event start="T1396-562" end="T537">To pa to pol, </event>
      <event start="T537" end="T538">pol sem bil že star osemintrideset let, </event>
      <event start="T538" end="T539">ko sem bil star enaindevetdesetega. </event>
      <event start="T539" end="T1402-974">Ko smo šli v vojno, </event>
      <event start="T1402-974" end="T1404-088">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T1404-088" end="T1405-344">Takrat s() ... </event>
      <event start="T1408-447" end="T1410-044">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T1410-044" end="T1412-037">jaz sem bil tankist v Pivki. </event>
      <event start="T1412-037" end="T1413-436">Petnajst mesecev gulil tisti prepih. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1418-897" end="T1420-989">Ja ja. [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1420-989" end="T541">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T541" end="T1423-557">to, k je zdaj hotel. </event>
      <event start="T1423-557" end="T1426-708">To v() to je imela čez jugo vojska. </event>
      <event start="T1426-708" end="T1428-858">Pa vojašnico Kranj. </event>
      <event start="T1428-858" end="T1430-407">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1430-407" end="T1431-856">Pa Jezersko gor. </event>
      <event start="T1433-046" end="T544">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T544" end="T599">to smo one vojake spucali, </event>
      <event start="T599" end="T1434-769">k so eni so se predali </event>
      <event start="T1434-769" end="T545">pa so to z avtobusi jih vozili, kamor je kdor hotel. </event>
      <event start="T545" end="T1442-013">Eni so bežali že prej. </event>
      <event start="T1442-013" end="T1443-61">Eee. </event>
      <event start="T1443-61" end="T1446-201">Pol na Jesenicah ... </event>
      <event start="T1446-201" end="T546">smo bili, k smo se malo ustrašili, </event>
      <event start="T546" end="T1450-26">ku vojska je zasedla mejni prehod. </event>
      <event start="T1450-866" end="T551">Eee </event>
      <event start="T551" end="T547">pa Pokljuko smo imeli </event>
      <event start="T547" end="T1460-171">pa v Radovljici ono ta veliko kasarno, ko so p() poveljstvo [glas] graničarjev je bilo tam. </event>
      <event start="T1460-667" end="T1461-65">Za ... vso Slovenijo, </event>
      <event start="T1461-65" end="T1463-287">rajtam. </event>
      <event start="T1467-876" end="T1468-518">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1486-245" end="T1487-902">Ja, ja. </event>
      <event start="T1495-404" end="T1496-288">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1510-131" end="T1512-402">Peč() da ni bil Pečovnik. </event>
      <event start="T1512-402" end="T560">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T560" end="T1514-712">samo to je ... </event>
      <event start="T1524-295" end="T1525-139">Aha. </event>
      <event start="T1531-056" end="T565">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T565" end="T1533-648">k tam je bilo več. </event>
      <event start="T1533-648" end="T566">Po so pa šli to na Virn() pod Virnikov Grintavec. </event>
      <event start="T566" end="T1539-264">Virnikova planina se reče. </event>
      <event start="T1539-264" end="T567">Tako() to so, </event>
      <event start="T567" end="T568">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T568" end="T1543-119">pet tisoč v() kvadratnih metrov ... je vojska tam odkupila, </event>
      <event start="T1543-119" end="T1547-559">tako da tisti kucelj je bil od vojske, </event>
      <event start="T1547-559" end="T1548-304">JLA. </event>
      <event start="T1548-76" end="T1552-823">In so tam delali to ta veliko stavbo za sto dvajset postelj. </event>
      <event start="T1552-823" end="T1555-885">Devetinosemdesetega leta je bilo to končano. </event>
      <event start="T1556-689" end="T569">Eee pa spodaj pod hišo, </event>
      <event start="T569" end="T570">trideset metrov je bilo poravnano kot v() fuzbalsko igrišče pa heliodrom, </event>
      <event start="T570" end="T1568-404">lahko so helikopterji tam pristajali. </event>
      <event start="T1568-404" end="T571">Eee ni bilo pa vse dokončano, </event>
      <event start="T571" end="T601">bilo plo() mmm recimo po dvorišču, </event>
      <event start="T601" end="T602">k je dosti placa, </event>
      <event start="T602" end="T572">toliko da si kamion lahko obračal t() tam, </event>
      <event start="T572" end="T1577-483">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T1577-483" end="T1580-793">So ti jaški od kanalizacije, </event>
      <event start="T1580-793" end="T573">pa [smeh] to so gledali takole ven. </event>
      <event start="T573" end="T1585-12">Ni() niso asfaltirali. </event>
      <event start="T1586-316" end="T575">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T575" end="T576">kuhinja je bila pa že uštimana, </event>
      <event start="T576" end="T577">in ta je bila od ona je bila vmes. </event>
      <event start="T577" end="T1594-036">Ker oni so vse do Tržiča hodili ob meji. </event>
      <event start="T1594-036" end="T578">Te patrulje, </event>
      <event start="T578" end="T1595-231">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T1595-687" end="T1597-341">Še pse so imeli. </event>
      <event start="T1597-341" end="T579">Nekaj časa. </event>
      <event start="T579" end="T581">Je bilo pa več tam, </event>
      <event start="T581" end="T580">ta pot. </event>
      <event start="T580" end="T582">Zdaj sem že pozabil, </event>
      <event start="T582" end="T583">včasih sem ono med vojno smo gledali, kje so oni hodili. </event>
      <event start="T583" end="T584">Vse smo vedeli, </event>
      <event start="T584" end="T1606-724">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T1606-724" end="T1610-608">K so imeli tudi telefone ž() napeljane, te njihove, </event>
      <event start="T1610-608" end="T1612-133">one, </event>
      <event start="T1612-133" end="T603">kva je že, </event>
      <event start="T603" end="T604">Rup tri </event>
      <event start="T604" end="T1613-184">ali kva je že bilo. </event>
      <event start="T1613-184" end="T1614-373">Tiste ruske. </event>
      <event start="T1614-373" end="T1615-502">Eee. </event>
    </tier>
